doc.after: The four mainstays of the economy are agriculture tourism offshore financial services and raising cattle There is substantial fishing activity although this industry does not bring in much foreign exchange Exports include copra kava beef cocoa and timber and imports include machinery and equipment foodstuffs and fuels In contrast mining activity is unsubstantial
